msgstr "Exentar de ausencias por retardo"

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.actions.server,name:hr_attendance_advanced.ir_cron_generate_absences_ir_actions_server
msgid "Generate automatic absences for delay in attendance"
msgstr "Generar ausencias automaticas por retardo en asistencia"

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_attendance_advanced.field_hr_attendance__is_time_delay
msgid ""
"If the check-in is out of time and the difference is bigger than the "
"tolerance time, it will mark the record and be considered in salary rules "
"related."
msgstr ""
"Si el check-in está fuera de tiempo y la diferencia es más grande que los "
"minutos de tolerancia, será marcada en el registro y considerada en las "
"reglas de salario correspondientes."

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_attendance_advanced.field_res_company__exclude_previous_work_time
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_attendance_advanced.field_res_config_settings__exclude_previous_work_time
msgid ""
"If this field is enabled, the hours worked before the start of the workday "
"will be exclude as overtime."
msgstr ""
"Si este campo esta activado, las horas trabajadas antes del inicio de la "
"jornada serán excluidas de tiempo extra."

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_attendance_advanced.field_hr_employee__exempt_absence_for_delay
msgid ""
"Indicates if the employee is exempt from generating absences due to delays."
msgstr ""
"Indica si un empleado esta exento de generar ausencias debido a retardos."

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_attendance_advanced.field_hr_leave__auto_generated
msgid "Indicates if the leave was generated automatically due to a delay."
msgstr "Indica si la ausencia fue generada automaticamente debido a retardo."

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hr_attendance_advanced.res_config_settings_view_form
msgid "Set time tolerance"
msgstr "Ajusta el tiempo de tolerancia"

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_attendance_advanced.field_res_company__tolerance_check_in
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:hr_attendance_advanced.field_res_config_settings__tolerance_check_in
msgid ""
"Specifies the tolerance time (in minutes) allowed for late check-ins. If an "
"employee checks in within this tolerance period, it will be considered on "
"time. This tolerance is used when processing attendance records and may also"
" impact salary calculations."
msgstr ""
"Especifica el tiempo de tolerancia (en minutos) permitido para retrasos en "
"el check in. Si un empleado registra su check in dentro del tiempo de "
"tolerancia, sera considerado a tiempo. Esta tolerancia es utilizada para "
"procesar registros de asistencia y quizas tambien impacte calculos de "
"salario"

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_attendance_advanced/models/hr_leave.py:0
msgid ""
"The absence is linked to an automatically generated attendance record. If "
"the absence is not valid, please reject it to prevent it from being "
"considered in the payroll."
msgstr ""
"La ausencia está vinculada a un registro de asistencia generado "
"automáticamente. Si la ausencia no es válida, rechácela para evitar que se "
"considere en la nómina."

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_attendance_advanced/models/hr_leave.py:0
msgid ""
"This leave request has been automatically generated due to a delay. Please "
"review it. If it is not valid, reject it to prevent it from being included "
"in payroll."
msgstr ""
"Esta solicitud de ausencia se ha generado automaticamente debido a un "
"retardo.Por favor revisela. Si no es valida, rechavela para evitar que sea "
"incluida en nómina."

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hr_attendance_advanced.res_config_settings_view_form
msgid ""
"This will to get the attendances out of time and will be considered in some "
"salary rules"
msgstr ""
"Esto traerá las asistencias fuera de tiempo y serán consideradas en algunas "
"reglas de salario."

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:hr_attendance_advanced.field_hr_attendance__is_time_delay
msgid "Time Delay?"
msgstr "¿Retardo?"

#. module: hr_attendance_advanced
#: model:ir.model,name:hr_attendance_advanced.model_hr_leave
msgid "Time Off"
